title: Dakine Jewel 26L Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Jewel 26L Pack in Carlotta.
Jewel 26L Pack Features:
- Side access padded laptop compartment
- Fits most 14" laptops
- Fleece lined sunglass pocket
- Organizer pocket
- Mesh side pockets
- Insulated cooler pocket
- Adjustable sternum strap
